        <span class="author-bio">7+ years as a B2B industrial pricing analyst. Built pricing variance models (LogMid vs. ArthAvg, DVP% tracking) and evaluated Pricefx, PROS, Vendavo, Alteryx, Power BI, and Sigma in production. This site reflects tools I've actually used, not vendor marketing copy.</span>
